title: Shamanic Drum Jam
description:
Shamanic Drum Jam is a virtual version of the mystic ethnic musical instrument Shamanic Drum. You can use it anywhere in the street jams or to joke with your friends and in your work when asked to do the impossible. And just enjoying in headphones, Shamanic Drum will always be with you and give instant sound meditation and relaxing. Enjoy the freedom of sound, no longer need to carry big musical instrument, in your android smartphone all that may be necessary to activate the application and play in the mountains, the sea, around the campfire or in the countryside. Go to jam with guitar sounds and other drums, as well as the sounds of synthesizers. You can have fun causing rain and setting up equipment using this app. With Shamanic Drum Jam you get a sound shaman, create! 

-= Features =-
- Multi Touch supported!!!
- Really Shamanic Drum Sounds. 
- Best mystic ethnic musical instrument Shamanic Drum always with you.
- High quality sound samples.
- Enjoy the music .
- Use in street music jams and jokes.
- Maximum volume.
- Implemented a dynamic volume, now sound more lively.
- Added multisampling.
